{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In March '39, the country was actually completely destroyed by German occupation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Germany occupied Bohemia and Moravia, and Slovakia, by mysterious way, became a independent, small republic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much, very much so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That actually changed my whole life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, not many people even now knew then the so-called independent Republic of Slovakia, which was only a small part of the original Czechoslovakian Republic.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hitler decided in 1939, in March '39, then Slovakia will become a independent Slovakian Republic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I actually found out because politics is my-- my hobby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then why did a mighty empire-- because Germany was really the strongest country in '38, '39 in Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And why would they give independence to a small Slovakian people, which were-- 2.5 million were Slovaks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not at the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought doing the war many times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the war, I had also few indications why it happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just a youngster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew the real reason why the big, mighty Germany occupied absolutely with power and strength Bohemia and Moravia, which is two sorts of Czechoslovakia, and they were called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Jews were taken immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish population of these two countries were 8,000 in Moravia-- in Bohemia, about 5,000 in Moravia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About 12 to 13 million people were from the population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Jews were about, I would say-- 80,000, 40-- about 140,000 to 150,000 Jews were living in the two part of Czechoslovakia which was completely occupied by Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Slovakia had about 60,000, 75,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't finish the-- because I was-- I was ready to go for four years because that was the four years course.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
